      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GIDEON MONELLI (4) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (30.13) behind Just A Piastri at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. CANYA CELESTE (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 9 length second (28.11) over 488m at Mandurah. Hard to beat again. JUST A SAPPHIRE (2) missed the frame latest when seventh at this track (30.69) but scored five back at this track (30.21). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Likely to be about the money. RIPPIN' RUBY (7) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
